# byjc.dev - Your Central Hub

Welcome to **byjc.dev**, the central hub for showcasing my work, projects, and online presence. This site is built with **Next.js**, **Tailwind CSS**, and **Contentlayer**, combining cutting-edge technologies to create a polished and professional platform that represents who I am as a developer.

